tionMaximumZoomLevel","fragments":[{"kind":"identifier","text":"MLNShapeSourceOptionMaximumZoomLevel"}],"title":"MLNShapeSourceOptionMaximumZoomLevel","abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"An "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"NSNumber"},{"type":"text","text":" object containing an integer; specifies the maximum zoom level at"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"which to create vector tiles. A greater value produces greater detail at high"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"zoom levels. The default value is 18."}],"url":"\/documentation\/maplibre\/mlnshapesourceoptionmaximumzoomlevel","kind":"symbol","role":"symbol"},"doc://org.swift.MyProject/documentation/MapLibre/MLNShapeSourceOptionBuffer":{"type":"topic","title":"MLNShapeSourceOptionBuffer","kind":"symbol","abstract":[{"text":"An ","type":"text"},{"code":"NSNumber","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":" object containing an integer; specifies the size of the tile","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"buffer on each side. A value of 0 produces no buffer. A value of 512 produces a","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"buffer as wide as the tile itself. Larger values produce fewer rendering","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"artifacts near tile edges and slower performance. The default value is 128.","type":"text"}],"identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNShapeSourceOptionBuffer","fragments":[{"kind":"identifier","text":"MLNShapeSourceOptionBuffer"}],"url":"\/documentation\/maplibre\/mlnshapesourceoptionbuffer","role":"symbol"}}}